  "subcategory": "browser",
  "additional_info": "Changelog:\r\nV1.6: Made the scrollbar button option actually look good and adjust size based on other options.\r\nV1.5.2: Changed margin option to size so that it would be more evident about what it does. Note that \"large\" is the same size at the normal size for the default when using FT Deepdark for some reason.\r\nV1.5.1: Code regarding borders removed when not in use. Added option for fading effects.\r\nV1.5: Added glow and shadow effects with related options.\r\nV1.4.1: Added separate color option for borders. Added size option for borders. Added alpha transparency option for borders. Added an option to enable or disable autohiding.\r\nV1.4: Added optional padding, enabled by default. Changed the name because I felt like it and the old one doesn't match the current focus.\r\nV1.3: Added various border options to play with.\r\nV1.2.2: Added color options and an option to enable or disable scrollbar arrows. Added option to reduce side margin to fix minor issue with certain custom themes.\r\nV1.2.1: Added option to choose between unrounded or rounded edges.\r\nV1.2: Prevents \"complete themes\" from modifying the appearance (in most cases).\r\nV1.1: Now fades between colors and transparencies on webpage elements such as text boxes (Getting the effect to work on the main scrollbars is another story).\r\nV1: Initial Release\r\n\r\nPlease leave feedback and suggestions.\r\n\r\nKnown issues:\r\nScrollbar arrows don't seem to work right on mac.",
  "style_tags": [],
  "css": "/* AGENT_SHEET */\r\n@namespace url(http://www.mozilla.org/keymaster/gatekeeper/there.is.only.xul);\r\n\r\n\r\n/* Autohides scrollbar */\r\nscrollbar[orient=\"vertical\"]:not(:hover),\r\nscrollbar[orient=\"horizontal\"]:not(:hover) {\r\n    opacity: /*[[ah]]*/ !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/*[[arrow]]*/\r\n/* Removes whitespace and allows scrollbar to appear */\r\n scrollbar {\r\n    position: relative !important;\r\n    -moz-appearance: none !important;\r\n    background: none !important;\r\n    z-index: 999999 !important;\r\n    transition: opacity 1s ease !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/* Appearance of scrollbar thumb */\r\n scrollbar thumb {\r\n    position: absolute !important;\r\n    -moz-appearance: none !important;\r\n    background: rgba(/*[[color]]*/.6) !important;\r\n    border-radius: /*[[radius]]*/ !important;\r\n    /*[[fade]]*/\r\n    /*[[border]]*/\r\n    /*[[glowshad]]*/\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/* Color of scrollbar thumb on mouseover */\r\n scrollbar thumb:hover {\r\n    background: rgba(/*[[color]]*/.8) !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/* Color of scrollbar when clicked */\r\n scrollbar thumb:active {\r\n    background: rgba(/*[[color]]*/1) !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/* Scrollbar sizes */\r\n scrollbar[orient=\"vertical\"] {\r\n    margin-left: -/*[[margin]]*/px !important;\r\n}\r\n scrollbar[orient=\"horizontal\"] {\r\n    margin-top: -/*[[margin]]*/px !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n/*Scrollbar padding*/\r\n scrollbar[orient=\"vertical\"] {\r\n    padding: 0px /*[[padding]]*/px 0px 0px !important;\r\n}\r\n\r\n scrollbar[orient=\"horizontal\"] {\r\n    padding: 0px 0px /*[[padding]]*/px 0px !important;\r\n}",
